dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile represents built up areas in settlements of Hungary. GeoX Kft. (2020). Built Areas, Hungary, 2021. GeoX Kft. Available at: https://purl.stanford.edu/zv206dh5986 This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
